   <script type="text/javascript">
    function getImages() {
             var soapHeader = '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>'
 
             soapHeader += '<soap:Envelope xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:soap="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/">'
             soapHeader += '<soap:Body><GetHomeImages xmlns="http://tempuri.org/" /></soap:Body></soap:Envelope>'
 
             var url = window.location.href;
 
             var postUrl = url.substring(0, url.lastIndexOf("/")) + '/HomeImages.asmx';
             var soapActionUrl = 'http://tempuri.org/GetHomeImages';
             var xmlhttp = null;
             if (window.XMLHttpRequest) {
                 xmlhttp = new XMLHttpRequest();
             }
             else if (window.ActiveXObject) {
                 xmlhttp = new ActiveXObject("Microsoft.XMLHTTP");
             }
             else {
                 xmlhttp = false;
             }
 
             xmlhttp.open('POST', postUrl, false);
             xmlhttp.setRequestHeader('Content-Type', 'text/xml; charset=utf-8');
             xmlhttp.setRequestHeader("Host", "localhost");
             xmlhttp.setRequestHeader("SOAPAction", soapActionUrl);
             xmlhttp.setRequestHeader("Content-Length", soapHeader.length);
             xmlhttp.send(soapHeader);
 
             if (xmlhttp) {
                 
                 var ResStr = xmlhttp.responseText;
                 ResStr = ResStr.replace(/&lt;/gi, "<");
                 ResStr = ResStr.replace(/&gt;/gi, ">");
                 var resultText = ResStr.substring(ResStr.indexOf("GetHomeImagesResult") + 20, ResStr.indexOf("/GetHomeImagesResult") - 1);
                 return resultText;
             }
             else {
                 alert("XMLHTTP Error");
             }
         }
 
 
         $(document).ready(function () {
 
             $('#cssmenu > ul > li ul').each(function (index, element) {
                 var count = $(element).find('li').length;
                 var content = '<span class="cnt">' + count + '</span>';
                 //$(element).closest('li').children('a').append(content);
             });
 
             $('#cssmenu ul ul li:odd').addClass('odd');
             $('#cssmenu ul ul li:even').addClass('even');
 
             $('#cssmenu > ul > li > a').click(function () {
 
                 var checkElement = $(this).next();
 
                 $('#cssmenu li').removeClass('active');
                 $(this).closest('li').addClass('active');
 
                 if ((checkElement.is('ul')) && (checkElement.is(':visible'))) {
                     $(this).closest('li').removeClass('active');
                     checkElement.slideUp('normal');
                 }
                 if ((checkElement.is('ul')) && (!checkElement.is(':visible'))) {
                     $('#cssmenu ul ul:visible').slideUp('normal');
                     checkElement.slideDown('normal');
                 }
 
                 if ($(this).closest('li').find('ul').children().length == 0) {
                     return true;
                 } else {
                     return false;
                 }
 
             });
 
         });
 
         (function (lib, img, cjs) {
 
             var p; // shortcut to reference prototypes
 
             var imageList = getImages();
             var imagesArray = imageList.split(',');
 
             var image1 = imagesArray[0];
             var image2 = imagesArray[1];
             var image3 = imagesArray[2];
 
             // library properties:
             lib.properties = {
                 width: 600,
                 height: 181,
                 fps: 24,
                 color: "#FFFFFF",
                 manifest: [
 		            { src: image1, id: "img1" },
 		            { src: image2, id: "img2" },
 		            { src: image3, id: "img3" }
 	            ]
             };
 
 
             // symbols:
             (lib.img1 = function () {
                 this.initialize(img.img1);
             }).prototype = p = new cjs.Bitmap();
             p.nominalBounds = new cjs.Rectangle(0, 0, 400, 300);
 
             (lib.img2 = function () {
                 this.initialize(img.img2);
             }).prototype = p = new cjs.Bitmap();
             p.nominalBounds = new cjs.Rectangle(0, 0, 400, 366);
 
             (lib.img3 = function () {
                 this.initialize(img.img3);
             }).prototype = p = new cjs.Bitmap();
             p.nominalBounds = new cjs.Rectangle(0, 0, 448, 336);
 
             // stage content:
             (lib.staug_working = function () {
                 this.initialize();
                 // left image
                 this.shape = new cjs.Shape();
                 this.shape.graphics.f().s("#000000").ss(4, 1, 1).p("A8gOTIcl8lIcccaIgLAL");
                 this.shape.setTransform(184.5, 93.6);
 
                 this.shape_1 = new cjs.Shape();
                 this.shape_1.graphics.bf(img.img1, null, new cjs.Matrix2D(0.881, 0, 0, 0.869, -180.6, -110.2)).s().p("A8gOTIcl8lIcccaIgLALg");
                 this.shape_1.setTransform(184.5, 93.6);
 
                 // top image
                 this.shape_2 = new cjs.Shape();
                 this.shape_2.graphics.f().s("#000000").ss(4, 1, 1).p("AAlgkIhJBJ");
                 this.shape_2.setTransform(311.2, 136.3);
 
                 this.shape_3 = new cjs.Shape();
                 this.shape_3.graphics.bf(img.img3, null, new cjs.Matrix2D(1, 0, 0, 1, -215.5, -122.9)).s().p("A7TtrMA2nAAAI7UbXg");
                 this.shape_3.setTransform(320, 46.9);
 
                 // right image
                 this.shape_4 = new cjs.Shape();
                 this.shape_4.graphics.f().s("#000000").ss(4, 1, 1).p("A8hSVMAkogkpIUbUZ");
                 this.shape_4.setTransform(452.6, 69.3);
 
                 this.shape_5 = new cjs.Shape();
                 this.shape_5.graphics.bf(img.img2, null, new cjs.Matrix2D(1,0,0,1,-200,-150)).s().p("A8hSVMAkogkpIUbUZIAAQQg");
                 this.shape_5.setTransform(452.6, 69.3);
 
 
                 //keep code to compare to check what bit zooms
 
                 //this.addChild(this.shape_5, this.shape_4, this.shape_3, this.shape_2, this.shape_1, this.shape);
                 this.addChild(this.shape_5, this.shape_4, this.shape_1, this.shape);
             }).prototype = p = new cjs.Container();
             p.nominalBounds = new cjs.Rectangle(317, 42.5, 637.3, 238.7);
 
         })(lib = lib || {}, images = images || {}, createjs = createjs || {});
         var lib, images, createjs;
         
         var canvas, stage, exportRoot;
 
         function init() {
             canvas = document.getElementById("canvasTri");
 
             var context = canvas.getContext('2d');
 
             context.clearRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height);
 
 
 
             //context.clearRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height);
 
             images = images || {};
 
             var loader = new createjs.LoadQueue(false);
             loader.addEventListener("fileload", handleFileLoad);
             loader.addEventListener("complete", handleComplete);
             loader.loadManifest(lib.properties.manifest);
         }
 
         function handleFileLoad(evt) {
             if (evt.item.type == "image") { images[evt.item.id] = evt.result; }
         }
 
         function handleComplete() {
             exportRoot = new lib.staug_working();
 
             stage = new createjs.Stage(canvas);
             stage.addChild(exportRoot);
             stage.update();
 
             createjs.Ticker.setFPS(lib.properties.fps);
         }
         function ScrollDiv() {
 
             if (document.getElementById('eventsDiv').scrollTop < (document.getElementById('eventsDiv').scrollHeight - document.getElementById('eventsDiv').offsetHeight)) {
                 -1
                 document.getElementById('eventsDiv').scrollTop = document.getElementById('eventsDiv').scrollTop + 1
             }
             else { document.getElementById('eventsDiv').scrollTop = 0; }
         }
 
         setInterval(ScrollDiv, 80)
   </script>
